{"tid":158330,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【補強防線】教授點名買蘇超後衛","createTime":"2017-03-16T07:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T11:11:27.000Z","uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"242e5538fa4f9a3333c1a4fe44d7c65c8849ae4d","tid":158330,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:53:40.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴的防守能力，一直飽受詬病，要求雲格加強防線實力的聲音，一直都沒有停過。而今阿仙奴的目標浮出了水面，雲格盯上了些路迪後衛基蘭-蒂爾內。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據《太陽報》報導，阿仙奴準備挖角些路迪後衛基蘭-蒂爾內，雲格準備用他來加強球隊的後防線。基蘭-蒂爾內目前19歲，2015年4月他上演了一線隊首戰，隨後的兩年，他的實力取得了穩步增長。<br />\n<br />\n　　《太陽報》表示，雲格希望用基蘭-蒂爾內作為蒙利爾的替代者，並且能夠和基比斯形成競爭，籍此來提高阿仙奴的防線實力。今年一月份，曼聯也曾派遣球探去觀看基蘭-蒂爾內的比賽，紅魔對這位年輕後衛，也有興趣。"},{"pid":"f13df492949a9f29600d04c9bc938de496e46a9a","tid":158330,"uid":2697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"19歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e42be94c3b2f18604ea3dbea644a0454b156740","tid":158330,"uid":69680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:52:00.000Z","msg":"又幻齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac84e59853e869cb70f007b8c695576c184a26f","tid":158330,"uid":65016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又幻齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲加條仆街有戀童癖......"},{"pid":"e7d0f330b9a7dcb2c0f40f693b59e064979921b4","tid":158330,"uid":57049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:05:48.000Z","msg":"成日買啲後生仔返嚟踢唔掂一係流放一係借走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea59edb55b69d07a29b3189e5c533a87fb53ba5a","tid":158330,"uid":40818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:11:27.000Z","msg":"玩厭左浩鼎， 走去買個19歲返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}